== Description ==
Nubo is a Belgian cooperation which was founded in January 2019. Its aim is to become a more ethical and sustainable alternative to traditional cloud storage and  email providers.
Funding in order to start building infrastructure was secured in December 2019.

Beta testers were invited to start testing the service starting Januari 2021.

In January 2022 the service was opened to the general public.

